\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
The container-fluid class places content inside of a container that will
 always be the width of the screen.
 This is helpful for scenarios where the content to be displayed must use
 the entire browser window.
\end_layout

\end_inset
</cell>
</row>
